snippet.title: Super Indie Karts 2018 Ultra Update Promo 1080 VHS
snippet.description:
Promo trailer for the first Ultra Update to Super Indie Karts, found footage on a long lost old VHS tape at the back of the garage! ;)

The Emerald Cup features races in the SIK Ultra Stadium, Teslagrad's Tesla Tower Floor 64, Canabalt's City Circuit, and Runbow Road 64.

Game available at https://store.steampowered.com/app/323670/Super_Indie_Karts/ - Ultra Update available July19th!

TRAILER MUSIC: 
Drive by Alex featuring cdk & Darryl J - http://ccmixter.org/files/AlexBeroza/43098 
CC Attribution (3.0) - https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
